### ============================================================
### Payments V2
### Base URL: https://localhost:49609
###
### Payment is auto-created when an order is placed (via OrderPlacedHandler).
### The only manual action here is confirming payment (MaintenanceRole).
###
### Flow:
###   1. POST /api/v2/orders       → order placed → payment created automatically
###   2. GET  /api/v2/payments/by-order/{orderId}  → find payment id
###   3. PUT  /api/v2/payments/confirm             → confirm → triggers PaymentConfirmed
###   4. PaymentConfirmedHandler   → order status → Paid
###   5. POST /api/v2/refunds      → request refund (refunds-v2.http)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = https://localhost:49609
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

# ============================================================
# AUTH
# ============================================================

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@localhost",
  "password": "aDminN@W25!"
}

###

# ============================================================
# PAYMENTS
# ============================================================

### Get payment by id
# Expected: 200 OK  →  PaymentDetailsVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get payment — not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get payment by order id
# Expected: 200 OK  →  PaymentDetailsVm
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/by-order/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Get payment by order — no payment for this order
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/by-order/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
###

### Confirm payment — happy path (MaintenanceRole)
# Expected: 200 OK
# paymentId: obtained from GET /by-order above
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "paymentId": 1,
  "transactionRef": "TXN-20260314-001"
}
###

### Confirm payment — without transaction reference
# Expected: 200 OK (transactionRef is optional)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "paymentId": 2,
  "transactionRef": null
}
###

### Confirm payment — already confirmed
# Expected: 409 Conflict  →  { "error": "Payment is already confirmed." }
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "paymentId": 1,
  "transactionRef": "TXN-DUPLICATE"
}
###

### Confirm payment — payment not found
# Expected: 404 Not Found  →  { "error": "Payment not found." }
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "paymentId": 99999,
  "transactionRef": null
}
###

### Confirm payment — expired window
# Expected: 409 Conflict  →  { "error": "Payment window has expired." }
# (requires a payment whose expiry job has already run)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payments/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "paymentId": 3,
  "transactionRef": "TXN-EXPIRED"
}
###
